## Implementation Details

The configuration matches the official Vercel documentation exactly:

```tsx
// app/layout.tsx
import { SpeedInsights } from "@vercel/speed-insights/next"

export default function RootLayout({ children }) {
  return (
    <html lang="en">
      <body>
        {children}
        <SpeedInsights />
      </body>
    </html>
  );
}
```

## Next Steps for Activation

To start collecting Speed Insights data:

1. **Enable in Vercel Dashboard**: Navigate to your project settings on Vercel and enable Speed Insights
2. **Deploy**: The feature is already deployed (previous PR #1)
3. **Monitor**: Data will appear in the Speed Insights dashboard after users visit your site

